snippet.textDisplay:
The advent of Islam in the Indian subcontinent through invasions & brutal conquest destroyed the old value systems & traditions of Punjab the cradle of dharma . The happy-go- lucky , hard working & colorful culture of Punjab , its people was reduced to wahabbhism as half of Punjab's native prople were converted to Islam & adopted abrahamic monotheism which precluded music , celebration, reverence for motherland, nature & ancestors & respect for ancestral traditions.  

For almost 900 yrs the spirit of Punjab was assaulted by the waves of invading barbarians from the northwest .... The true , native ancient spirit of Punjab today rests with age old dharmic values & traditions still preserved in Indian Punjab.  Pakistani Punjab is today a wahabbistan of religious orthodoxy where all dharmic people have either been converted to Islam or left that part & migrated away to safety ....
